<br>
I wax and wane with my time online, both on Lanys and Stormhammer, so I'm nowhere near the 8hrs/night crowd (and I'm not so sure we have any of those anyway.) <br>
<br>
So... being with your man IRL has got to be a priority, just remember that your Ordo chums will be pleased as punch for you to be happy in Norrath or that weird (otherworldly?) place called Massachusetts. And certainly being happy with your huzbear is all that much better. We'll still be there when you want to get away, or just have some fun barshin' stuff. We have many member who are only on every now and again, and they are just as much part of the Ordo Family as the power levellers... <br>
<br>
So take whatever time you need to adjust your life and play schedules, and be sure we'll keep the ovens and forges hot, and the mobs poppin' in SK or Oasis or LOIO or wherever... <br>
